; Coverage test for xact.cc line 918 and auto_xact_t::extend_xact
; Tests that an automatic transaction predicate correctly returns false
; for non-matching transactions.  The Transfer transaction does not match
; /Expenses:Food/, so the auto-xact is not applied to it.  The Groceries
; transaction matches and gets the auto-generated posting.

= /Expenses:Food/
    (Budget:Food)    -1.0

2024/01/01 Transfer
    Assets:Checking    $-100.00
    Assets:Savings     $100.00

2024/01/02 Groceries
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg
24-Jan-01 Transfer              Assets:Checking            $-100.00     $-100.00
                                Assets:Savings              $100.00            0
24-Jan-02 Groceries             Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
                                (Budget:Food)               $-10.00      $-10.00
end test
